Class ResourceEvent

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      sailpoint.object.SailPointObject
          sailpoint.object.ResourceEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject, sailpoint.tools.xml.XMLReferenceTarget
public class ResourceEvent
extends SailPointObject
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable

A class used to maintain a queue of change events received from Connectors that support change notification. These are normally created by the SMListenerService as it receives events from SM instances.
